---
title: Golden-Spiced Chicken Traybake with Pumpkin Wedges & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Create a family feast of colourful veggies and succulent chicken thigh. Our Aussie spice blend brings a moreish flavour to the chicken and veggies, while the dill-parsley mayo is perfect for dolloping over everything. Yum!
